{"word":"G3640 - ὀλιγόπιστος - oligópistos - ol-ig-op'-is-tos - Of little faith","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὀλιγόπιστος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>oligópistos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>ol-ig-op'-is-tos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Of little faith"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"அற்பவிசுவாசியான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"of little faith, trusting too little"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G3641 - ὀλίγος - olígos - ol-ee'-gos/3641\">G3641</a> and <a href=\"#/G4102 - πίστις - pístis - pis'-tis/4102\">G4102</a>; <i>incredulous</i>, that is, <i>lacking confidence</i> (in Christ): - of little faith."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3640 - ὀλιγόπιστος - oligópistos - ol-ig-op'-is-tos/3640\">G3640</a>, <a href=\"#/G3641 - ὀλίγος - olígos - ol-ee'-gos/3641\">G3641</a>, <a href=\"#/G3642 - ὀλιγόψυχος - oligópsychos - ol-ig-op'-soo-khos/3642\">G3642</a>, <a href=\"#/G3643 - ὀλιγωρέω - oligōréō - ol-ig-o-reh'-o/3643\">G3643</a>, <a href=\"#/G4100 - πιστεύω - pisteúō - pist-yoo'-o/4100\">G4100</a>, <a href=\"#/G4102 - πίστις - pístis - pis'-tis/4102\">G4102</a>, <a href=\"#/G4103 - πιστός - pistós - pis-tos'/4103\">G4103</a>, <a href=\"#/G4104 - πιστόω - pistóō - pis-to'-o/4104\">G4104</a>, <a href=\"#/G569 - ἀπιστέω - apistéō - ap-is-teh'-o/569\">G569</a>, <a href=\"#/G570 - ἀπιστία - apistía - ap-is-tee'-ah/570\">G570</a>, <a href=\"#/G571 - ἄπιστος - ápistos - ap'